query: SELECT et.id, et.targetType, et.customName, et.targetValue, et.currentValue, et.baseValue, et.month, et.year, et.status FROM employees e JOIN employeeTargets et ON e.id = et.employeeId WHERE e.name LIKE '%غادة%' AND et.year = 2026 AND et.month = 2;
